    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>世界一片黑暗与空虚。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《暗黑森林》</strong>是一款点击放置类恐怖游戏，使你向内叩问灵魂，向外探索未知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/691ff92c1d91b98ba91e52cf1e282e08.poster.avif?t=1749838155\" width=564 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/691ff92c1d91b98ba91e52cf1e282e08.webm?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/691ff92c1d91b98ba91e52cf1e282e08.mp4?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>黑暗触及的一切均为你所有。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><strong>探索世界，</strong>收集资源，在这片幽深的森林中建立你的家园。<br><i>记住…黑暗永不眠，它不欢迎挑战它的不速之客。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/ca716eecb90a3296f635a88bc5ca11cd.poster.avif?t=1749838155\" width=252 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/ca716eecb90a3296f635a88bc5ca11cd.webm?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/ca716eecb90a3296f635a88bc5ca11cd.mp4?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>救世主，还是暴君？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/88376e38400c40241cd7160ecca44653.poster.avif?t=1749838155\" width=352 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/88376e38400c40241cd7160ecca44653.webm?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/88376e38400c40241cd7160ecca44653.mp4?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>击败11只深渊生物。</strong>是宽恕，还是处决它们？<br>每个选择都将带来后果…<i>全8种结局，你有没有胆量解锁</i>？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/d2c5395d4516960f33f8eed3c94737b2.poster.avif?t=1749838155\" width=540 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/d2c5395d4516960f33f8eed3c94737b2.webm?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/d2c5395d4516960f33f8eed3c94737b2.mp4?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精心管理！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br><strong>指挥无面众生。</strong>体验不同资源生产链策略，决定你的统治方式！ <br><i>是铁腕统治？有限自治与自由？还是建立神秘的共济会？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/1d69f28bf5fe7f9e8aef1d61265e42de.poster.avif?t=1749838155\" width=344 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/1d69f28bf5fe7f9e8aef1d61265e42de.webm?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/1d69f28bf5fe7f9e8aef1d61265e42de.mp4?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亲爱的日记…</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br>一波未平，一波又起。你是会塑造这个世界，还是被它所塑造？<br><i>是见好就收？还是纵容永无止境的贪欲？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/a258e73fc013b78a786c2f5278a01e70.poster.avif?t=1749838155\" width=282 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/a258e73fc013b78a786c2f5278a01e70.webm?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314970/extras/a258e73fc013b78a786c2f5278a01e70.mp4?t=1749838155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
